msgid "<b style=\"font-size: 16px;\">AP Wired Relay Enabled:</b><br>1. DHCP will be disabled. <b style=\"color: #059669;\">Devices must use static IPs or get IPs from upstream.</b><br>2. If LAN IP changes, ensure your client is in the same subnet to avoid <b style=\"color: #059669;\">losing access</b>."
