msgstr "检测到上级网络分配的地址 ({wan_ip}) 与本路由器的内网 ({lan_ip}) 发生严重冲突！<br><br>必须修改本设备的 LAN IP。系统建议安全避让至：<b>{safe_ip}</b>"

msgid "Severe Physical Conflict"
msgstr "⚠️ 严重物理冲突"

msgid "The WAN Static IP ({ip}) you set is exactly the same as the upstream Gateway!<br><br>This causes a severe physical loop. Please change your Static IP (e.g., {suggest_ip})."
msgstr "您设置的 WAN 静态 IP ({ip}) 与上级网络的真实网关完全相同！<br><br>这将导致严重的物理死环。请修改您的静态 IP（例如改为 {suggest_ip}）。"

msgid "The AP IP ({ip}) you set is exactly the same as the upstream Gateway!<br><br>This will paralyze the network. Please change to another free IP (e.g., {suggest_ip})."
msgstr "您设置的旁路由 IP ({ip}) 与上级网络的真实网关完全相同！<br><br>这将导致全屋网络瘫痪。请修改为同网段的其他空闲 IP（例如 {suggest_ip}）。"

