msgstr "高级与实验室功能"

msgid "Beta"
msgstr "测试"

msgid "Full Software Backup & Restore"
msgstr "全量软件的备份与恢复"

msgid "Resolves traditional backup soft-brick risks. Smart backup is cross-version compatible. After flashing new firmware, upload backup to <span style=\"color:#ef4444; font-weight:bold;\">restore all software and configs perfectly (Requires Internet)</span>. Does not delete current software during restore. For absolute purity, factory reset router first.<br>If Netwiz is missing after reset, run this in SSH:"
msgstr "解决传统备份容易导致死机、软砖风险，智能备份兼容跨版本恢复。刷入新固件后，上传备份即可<span style=\"color:#ef4444; font-weight:bold;\">极速重装所有软件并无损还原配置（需联网）</span>。恢复时不会删除当前软件。若需达到绝对纯净，请先恢复出厂设置。<br>恢复出厂后若未安装 Netwiz，可联网后在终端执行："

msgid "Generate Backup"
msgstr "生成备份文件"

msgid "Restore System"
msgstr "恢复系统软件"

msgid "Click to Copy"
msgstr "点击复制"

msgid "Copied"
msgstr "已复制"

msgid "Copy Failed"
msgstr "复制失败"

msgid "Select Backup Mode"
msgstr "选择备份模式"

msgid "Lightweight Backup"
msgstr "轻量化备份"

msgid "Recommended"
msgstr "推荐模式"

msgid "Full Backup"
msgstr "全量备份"

msgid "Includes Dependencies"
msgstr "包含深层依赖"

msgid "<b style=\"color: #F00;\">Lightweight Backup:</b> Only packs core configs (Passwords/Wi-Fi/IP) and main plugin packages. Fast and requires no extra RAM. Requires internet or built-in dependencies when restoring."
msgstr "<b style=\"color: #F00;\">轻量化备份说明:</b> 仅打包核心配置(账号密码/无线/IP)和主插件包，不抓取底层深层依赖，速度极快。恢复时新固件需自带对应依赖或处于联网状态。"

msgid "<b style=\"color: #F00;\">Full Backup:</b> Packs core configs and recursively downloads ALL underlying dependencies for third-party plugins. Large size, slower generation. <b style=\"color: #F00;\">NO internet required</b> during restore. Recommended for devices with >256MB RAM."
msgstr "<b style=\"color: #F00;\">全量备份说明:</b> 递归下载所有第三方插件的完整底层依赖。体积庞大生成较慢，优点是恢复时<b style=\"color: #F00;\">完全不需要网络</b>即可重装成功。建议内存 >256M 的设备使用。"

msgid "Start Backup"
msgstr "确定开始备份"

msgid "Generating Backup"
msgstr "正在生成备份"

msgid "Extracting configs and packing files in background..."
msgstr "正在后台提取配置并打包文件..."

msgid "Note: Full mode selected, downloading all dependencies. Takes 1-3 mins, please wait."
msgstr "提示: 当前为全量模式，需要下载全部底层依赖。大约需 1 到 3 分钟，请耐心等待。"

msgid "Note: Lightweight mode selected, packing is very fast (~30s)."
msgstr "提示: 当前为轻量模式，打包速度极快。大约需要 30 秒左右。"

msgid "Backup Successful"
msgstr "打包成功"

msgid "Backup capsule downloaded. Upload this file after flashing new firmware to restore."
msgstr "备份胶囊已成功下载。刷入新系统后上传此文件即可恢复。"

msgid "Backup Failed"
msgstr "打包失败"

msgid "Unable to start background backup task."
msgstr "无法启动后台备份任务"

msgid "Confirm System Restore"
msgstr "确认恢复系统"

msgid "<span style=\"color:#ef4444; font-weight:bold;\">WARNING: This will overwrite current configs and reinstall plugins!</span><br><br>Router will auto-reboot upon completion. Ensure file is correct.<br><br>"
msgstr "<span style=\"color:#ef4444; font-weight:bold;\">⚠️ 安全警告：此操作具有最高系统权限，将彻底覆盖当前配置！</span><br><br><span style=\"color:#f59e0b; font-weight:bold;\">防黑客提示：请绝对不要上传来自论坛或陌生人提供的来路不明备份文件，否则您的路由器可能会被植入木马后门！</span><br><br>恢复完成后路由器将自动重启。<br><br>"

msgid "Auto-download current state backup before restore (Regret Pill)"
msgstr "恢复前先自动下载当前状态的备份 (后悔药)"

msgid "Confirm & Select File"
msgstr "确认并选择文件"

msgid "Native Fast Restore Mode"
msgstr "原生极速恢复模式"

msgid "Transferring capsule via high-speed system channel...<br><br><b style=\"color:#ef4444;\">DO NOT power off. Router will auto-reboot upon completion.</b>"
msgstr "正在调用系统底层高速通道直传胶囊...<br><br><b style=\"color:#ef4444;\">请勿断开电源，路由器将在完成后自动重启。</b>"

msgid "Capsule delivered, preparing offline task..."
msgstr "胶囊已送达底层，准备执行脱机任务..."

msgid "Restore Blocked by Security"
msgstr "恢复异常被安全拦截"

msgid "Self-healing mechanism triggered. Garbage cleared, router is safe and unharmed."
msgstr "系统已启动自愈机制清理了垃圾残留，您的路由器目前处于安全状态，并未受损。"

msgid "Transfer Failed"
msgstr "传输失败"

msgid "Interface rejected reception, status code: "
msgstr "底层接口拒绝接收，状态码: "

msgid "Network Error"
msgstr "网络错误"

msgid "File transfer interrupted unexpectedly, check network!"
msgstr "文件传输被意外中断，请检查网络连线！"

msgid "Preparing Regret Pill"
msgstr "正在为您调配后悔药"

msgid "Backing up current state to prevent regrets...<br><br><span style=\"font-size:12px; color:#10b981;\">Tip: Restore will begin automatically after download</span>"
msgstr "正在备份当前系统状态以防恢复后反悔<br><br><span style=\"font-size:12px; color:#10b981;\">提示: 备份下载完成后将自动开始覆盖并恢复新系统</span>"

msgid "Probing Environment"
msgstr "正在探测运行环境"

msgid "Calculating system available RAM and storage..."
msgstr "正在计算系统可用内存与存储空间..."

msgid "Critical RAM Shortage"
msgstr "物理内存严重不足"

msgid "Your full capsule size is <b style=\"color:#ef4444;\">{size} MB</b>.<br><br>But /tmp (RAM) only has <b style=\"color:#ef4444;\">{avail} MB</b> free!<br><br>Force uploading will <b style=\"color:#f00;\">cause OOM, crash, and network drop</b>.<br><br><b>Solution:</b> Please <b style=\"color:#10b981;\">reboot the router</b> once to clear RAM fragments, then retry."
msgstr "检测到您的全量胶囊大小为 <b style=\"color:#ef4444;\">{size} MB</b>。<br><br>但当前路由器的 /tmp (运行内存) 仅剩余 <b style=\"color:#ef4444;\">{avail} MB</b> 可用空间！<br><br>强行上传将<b style=\"color:#f00;\">导致路由器内存溢出、死机并断网</b>。<br><br><b>解决方案：</b>请先<b style=\"color:#10b981;\">重启一次路由器</b>来清空内存碎片，重启后再进行恢复操作。"

msgid "Cancel Restore"
msgstr "取消恢复"

msgid "Waiting for background task to start..."
msgstr "等待后台任务启动..."

msgid "Capsule delivered, initializing restore environment..."
msgstr "胶囊已送达，正在初始化恢复环境..."

msgid "Scanning capsule structure to estimate uncompressed size (5-10s)..."
msgstr "正在扫描胶囊深层结构以预估解压体积 (约需 5-10 秒)..."

msgid "Uncompressed size reaches {u}MB, but RAM only has {a}MB left! Intercepted to prevent router crash."
msgstr "解压体积达 {u}MB，但内存仅剩 {a}MB！为防止死机，已触发安全拦截。"

msgid "Size safe! Extracting backup capsule..."
msgstr "体积安全！正在解压备份胶囊..."

msgid "Extraction failed! Capsule may be corrupted, initiating self-healing..."
msgstr "解压失败！可能是压缩包损坏，已启动自愈机制清理内存。"

msgid "Extraction successful, applying core configs..."
msgstr "解压成功，正在覆盖系统核心配置..."

msgid "Force offline installing plugins (this takes a while, please wait)..."
msgstr "正在强制离线覆盖插件 (此过程较长，请耐心等待)..."

msgid "Restore thoroughly complete! Router will auto-reboot!"
msgstr "恢复彻底完成！路由器即将自动重启！"

msgid "MSG_RST_INVALID"
msgstr "无效的胶囊文件！系统未检测到 NetWiz 专属特征码，为保护系统安全已自动拦截并销毁。"

msgid "File Too Large"
msgstr "文件过大"

msgid "<div style=\"text-align:left; color:#ef4444; font-weight:bold;\">Config files are usually under 100KB!</div><br>The selected file is too large and has been blocked."
msgstr "<div style=\"text-align:left; color:#ef4444; font-weight:bold;\">配置文件通常小于 100KB！</div><br>您选择的文件过大，已被安全拦截。"

msgid "Restore Network Config"
msgstr "还原网络配置"

msgid "This action will overwrite the existing network configuration and restart the network.<br><br><span style=\"color:#f59e0b; font-weight:bold;\">⚠️ Security Warning: Do not upload backups from unknown sources to prevent router hijacking.</span><br><br>Confirm restore?"
msgstr "此操作将覆盖现有的网络配置，并重启网络。<br><br><span style=\"color:#f59e0b; font-weight:bold;\">⚠️ 安全警告：请勿上传来路不明的备份文件，以免路由器被恶意劫持。</span><br><br>确认要执行还原吗？"

msgid "Restoring"
msgstr "正在还原"

msgid "Restore Failed"
msgstr "还原失败"

msgid "Error: "
msgstr "错误: "

msgid "Invalid Format"
msgstr "格式无效"

msgid "The uploaded file is not a valid JSON format and cannot be parsed!"
msgstr "您上传的文件不是有效的 JSON 格式，无法解析！"

msgid "Import Configuration"
msgstr "导入配置"

msgid "Are you sure you want to import this configuration? Existing data will be overwritten."
msgstr "确认要导入该配置吗？现有数据将被彻底覆盖。"

msgid "🚨 Severe Network Topology Conflict!"
msgstr "🚨 严重网络拓扑冲突！"

msgid "System detected that IPv6 and LAN \"Masquerading (NAT)\" are <b>BOTH enabled</b>!<br>This will paralyze IPv6 allocation and cause routing loops.<br>👉 <b>Fix:</b> Please <b style=\"color:#ef4444;\">Disable IPv6</b> here immediately, or go to <code>Network -> Firewall</code> to disable NAT."
msgstr "系统检测到 IPv6 与 LAN 区“动态伪装 (NAT)”<b>同时处于开启状态</b>！<br>这将导致 IPv6 分配瘫痪与路由死循环。<br>👉 <b>排错指南：</b>请前往官方 <code>网络->防火墙</code> 关闭 LAN 区的动态伪装，或在此处 <b style=\"color:#ef4444;\">关闭 IPv6</b>，。"

msgid "⚠️ IPv6 Configuration Blocked"
msgstr "⚠️ IPv6 配置已被系统安全拦截"

msgid "Detected that LAN \"IP Masquerading (NAT)\" is enabled. Forcing IPv6 on under a double-NAT topology will cause network disconnection.<br>👉 <b>Fix:</b> Please go to <code>Network -> Firewall -> Zones</code> to disable LAN Masquerading first."
msgstr "检测到防火墙 LAN 区已开启“IP 动态伪装 (NAT)”。在双重 NAT 拓扑下，强行开启 IPv6 将导致断网。<br>👉 <b>排错指南：</b>请前往官方后台 <code>网络->防火墙->区域</code>，关闭 LAN 区的动态伪装后重试。"
